<span class="head">2002 Best of CES Award Winners</span><br><br> 


At the 2002 CES, the TechTV-appointed panel of product evaluators selected winners in each category according to their innovative appeal, usability, usefulness and affordability. In addition to the 12 category winners, a single product was honored as Best of Show. <br><br>

<center><span class="head">BEST OF SHOW</span>
<BR><BR>
<font size="2"><strong>Moxi Digital, Inc. / Moxi Media Center / Home media server</font></strong>
</center>
<br><br>
<span class="subhead">Portable Audio and Video</span><br>
<strong>Winner:</strong>
<br>
SONICblue / Rio Riot / 20 gigabyte portable MP3 player 
<br><br>
<strong>Finalists:</strong>
<br>
<ul>
	<li> Sony Electronics Inc. / DCR-1P5 / a tiny digital video camera 
	<li> Panasonic Consumers Electronic Co. / SV-AV10 / 4-IN-1 A / V SD R 
</ul>
<br>
<span class="subhead">High-End Audio</span>
<br>
<strong>Winner:</strong>
<br>
VMPS Audio Products / Ribbon RM-40 / great sounding speakers with ribbon-cable tweeter
<br><br>
<strong>Finalists:</strong> 
<ul>
	<li> Arcam / AV8 / a pre-amp surround processor 
	<li> ERAUDIO Ltd. / STONE TWINS ER PRA 1 / high-end hand-built audio system from Russia 
</ul>
<br>
<span class="subhead">Home Theater</span>
